### Variaveis de Ambiente

@hostname=localhost
@port=8000

@BASE_URL={{hostname}}:{{port}}


### Listar todos os itens do estoque

GET http://{{BASE_URL}}/estoque HTTP/1.1
Accept: application/json

### Adicionar novo item no estoque 
POST http://{{BASE_URL}}/estoque HTTP/1.1
Content-Type : application/json
Accept: application/json

{
    "seller_id": "4",
    "sku": "Tv Smart LG",
    "quantidade": 10
}

### Buscar item pelo seller_id e sku 
GET http://{{BASE_URL}}/estoque/1/Mouse%20Gamer HTTP/1.1
Accept: application/json


### Buscar itens no estoque pelo seller_id com paginação
GET {{BASE_URL}}/estoque/buscar/?seller_id=1&page=1&page_size=10
Accept: application/json

### Buscar itens no estoque pelo sku com paginação
GET http://{{BASE_URL}}/estoque/buscar/?sku=Mouse%20Gamer&page=1&page_size=10"
Accept: application/json


### Atualizar um item no estoque
PUT  http://{{BASE_URL}}/estoque/1/Mouse%20Gamer HTTP/1.1
Content-Type : application/json
Accept: application/json

{
    "seller_id": "1",
    "sku": "Mouse Gamer",
    "quantidade": 25
}